Allows you to specify a set of build configuration values.
values set in build profile:
    1. can be in addition to what is in POM.xml
    2. or used to override existing pom values.
More than one profile can be set to active at a time

Build Profile allows you to change the behaviour of the build.
Build behaviour can be changed based on:
    1. the outcome of the build.
    2. Automatically based on the runtime enviornment
    3. Automatically to adapt the different OS
    4. To optionally Activate Specific Plugin
    5. To provide alternative build time configuration values.

